    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Associated with the Frankfurt School of critical sociology founded in 1923, it refers to the exercise of negative judgment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
